{"tid":887634,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]火影忍者 疾風亂舞(153)","createTime":"2018-11-03T05:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T07:49:08.000Z","uid":60591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"89eacde0a1da83eea888359e670f7de901c3c825","tid":887634,"uid":60591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>官網</strong> (附ios/an下載點) <br />\n<a href=\"http://narucole.jp/?at=1l3vkMx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnarucole.jp%2F%3Fat%3D1l3vkMx&d=nfzWDI8azAY8tkzr8OBsXdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=59cabc5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://narucole.jp/?at=1l3vkMx</a> <br />\n<strong>官方email address</strong><br />\nnarucole@help.gree.net <br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.bangqu.com/r2/news/20171121/30486b4169517a33504e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.bangqu.com%2Fr2%2Fnews%2F20171121%2F30486b4169517a33504e.jpg&h=7861289c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>官方宣傳GAMEPLAY</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M4fkx4Fu1uM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM4fkx4Fu1uM&d=nfzWDI8azAY8tkzr8OBsXdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=521a2167\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M4fkx4Fu1uM</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>攻略Wiki</strong> (日文,唔update): <br />\n<a href=\"http://naruto.upwiki.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnaruto.upwiki.net%2F&d=nfzWDI8azAY8tkzr8OBsXdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=26820d1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://naruto.upwiki.net/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>本post吉祥物</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WA94W0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WA94W0.jpg&h=1d99f3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9k4RbFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9k4RbFA.jpg&h=13546ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SfzAR5y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSfzAR5y.jpg&h=1321a9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>人人一抽入魂中新限</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所有好日唔上水 一上水就曬命嘅撚樣</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">古思堯</span></strong>有嘢同你哋講:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/092811_73cce7e19e693211f527fc268c42d3c1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F092811_73cce7e19e693211f527fc268c42d3c1.gif&h=6a64664e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*新手請睇曬post頭先發問*</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nPost頭目錄<br />\n1.首抽建議&amp;小知識<br />\n2.常見日文&amp;辭彙解釋<br />\n3.常見FAQ (紅字一定要睇)<br />\n4.疾風傳(主線任/物語任)拎石條件<br />\n5.無所屬隊介紹&amp;心得<br />\n6.曉隊介紹&amp;心得<br />\n7.PVP心得<br />\n<br />\n給新手的話:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n雖然入到黎見老玩家三句唔埋就屌營運點閪點撚狗, 但呢隻GAME 本身絕對係一個好遊戲, 無論畫風, 操作方法, 平衡性(目前為止)黎講可玩性都算唔錯。GAME名 &quot;collections&quot; says it all, 課金有課金玩法, 無課有無課玩法, 當佢儲卡GAME就好, 罕有角難出係定律黎, N抽唔到限止蝕好緊要, 因為金錢有限, 但限角就會不斷出, 今次追唔到總有一次會出你有愛既角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> That's the meaning of collections<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滿11忍揀技速 記住 記住 記住</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>課金注意事項 </strong><br />\n用日本itunes下載遊戲再轉地區做香港課金, 會出現遊戲更新唔到嘅情況, 所以最好都係買日本itunes卡<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/012321_694633098564f786e86a06fb58f938cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F012321_694633098564f786e86a06fb58f938cf.png&h=072fa906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>假首抽</strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(雲上巴提供)</span><br />\n而家一入game，要先睇嗚佐大戰一輪<br />\n之後就可以係到揀一隻作為假首抽<br />\n而且會送兩個忍具<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/021123_6bafca7dbb1193ba33191eb9cad23875.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F021123_6bafca7dbb1193ba33191eb9cad23875.png&h=728f128b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>共鳴</strong><br />\n比較推薦新手既你揀共鳴<br />\n隊長技係知，勇屬Hp同技傷加多40%<br />\n最好地方係佢被動技一會加一技速<br />\n雖然做唔到雙閃但起碼令到佢技二閃光到先<br />\n<br />\n技二係上狀態共鳴最多係三次<br />\n每次加技傷20%同攻擊40%<br />\n最令人亮眼地方係查克拉大回復<br />\n<br />\n技一全體傷，而且係必中<br />\n加上令到佢雙閃忍具唔難拎<br />\n只要打天天忍具關就拎到佢件外套(加一技速)<br />\n總括而言前期佢又可以輸出又可以做補師<br />\n<br />\n<strong>十拳</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/015518_c3d8954c275099ffe036f49bf189d639.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F015518_c3d8954c275099ffe036f49bf189d639.png&h=063a2102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十拳係pvp較多人用，若果你自問覺得自己會係真首抽到抽到好野可以選擇佢<br />\n<br />\n隊長技係曉隊攻擊30% 狀態異常同弱体輕減<br />\n呢d通通都唔係重點<br />\n重點在於佢既被動技Hp 素早100% 減半查<br />\n正正係減半查導致佢只要配合忍具就可以做到0查出技<br />\n<br />\n技1 耐性無視+ 高機率封印<br />\n但用完減70%血。但傷害真係好高<br />\n係pvp直頭係秒殺<br />\n但係平時打關由於好boss都有幾條血或者多血情況下，好容易用一，兩下技一就比人打死<br />\n<br />\n技二係上狀態<br />\n減人攻，防，素早70%<br />\n不過並唔係好多時到上到<br />\n<br />\n你可能成日聽到老手講十拳點勁點強<br />\n係因為我地有忍具同其他隊員撘配<br />\n十拳只要忍具你有大南，pvp眼，其他放曬加素早既忍具就已經跑得好快<br />\n<br />\n新手並不建議選擇十拳作為假首抽<br />\n係因為你打關會好吃力<br />\n再加上難而做到雙閃<br />\n除非你有信心會係真首抽到中到好勁角色<br />\n唔係你花好多時間去培育其他角色<br />\n但無可否認十拳係pvp既mvp<br />\n<br />\n<strong>小知識</strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(雲上巴,藍b巴,肥毒巴,M巴提供)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/015502_7c6196ff18c25ba2e48ce6cb8a10868a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F015502_7c6196ff18c25ba2e48ce6cb8a10868a.jpg&h=0ad4327d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/014606_b06368a8424ebf43ee799d296a6be078.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F014606_b06368a8424ebf43ee799d296a6be078.png&h=5114a241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一張係5星忍道卷<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/014803_276cd6845dbdd5c51be72e51e8e6f48a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F014803_276cd6845dbdd5c51be72e51e8e6f48a.png&h=1e7c07ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係可以幫所有角色升一個忍道(除咗神忍，霸忍)，升爆忍道之後有唔同嘅強化畀你揀，通常黎講首選一定係<span style=\"color: gold;\">技速</span>(左下角)，可以更快出技，技能速度去到閃光就唔使行紅BAR 直接出技 呢樣喺PVP嚟講非常之重要<br />\n<br />\n唔同卡佢本身技速都唔同<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">(最慢)</span>激遲&gt;遲&gt;普通&gt;速&gt;最速&gt;閃光<span style=\"color: gold;\">(最快)</span><br />\n<br />\n每升一格就要+1技速，閃光=max<br />\n另外如果閃光+1，即使人地debuff 降你一階速都可以繼續閃光，如此類推<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙閃</span></strong>姐係 兩招技都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">閃光</span>"},{"pid":"81ac694ac9300bb0e793526f31395c840e113bbe","tid":887634,"uid":60591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:29:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>小知識</strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(雲上巴,藍b巴,肥毒巴,M巴提供)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/015502_7c6196ff18c25ba2e48ce6cb8a10868a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F015502_7c6196ff18c25ba2e48ce6cb8a10868a.jpg&h=0ad4327d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/014606_b06368a8424ebf43ee799d296a6be078.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F014606_b06368a8424ebf43ee799d296a6be078.png&h=5114a241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一張係5星忍道卷<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/014803_276cd6845dbdd5c51be72e51e8e6f48a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F014803_276cd6845dbdd5c51be72e51e8e6f48a.png&h=1e7c07ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係可以幫所有角色升一個忍道(除咗神忍，霸忍)，升爆忍道之後有唔同嘅強化畀你揀，通常黎講首選一定係<span style=\"color: gold;\">技速</span>(左下角)，可以更快出技，技能速度去到閃光就唔使行紅BAR 直接出技 呢樣喺PVP嚟講非常之重要<br />\n<br />\n唔同卡佢本身技速都唔同<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">(最慢)</span>激遲&gt;遲&gt;普通&gt;速&gt;最速&gt;閃光<span style=\"color: gold;\">(最快)</span><br />\n<br />\n每升一格就要+1技速，閃光=max<br />\n另外如果閃光+1，即使人地debuff 降你一階速都可以繼續閃光，如此類推<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙閃</span></strong>姐係 兩招技都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">閃光</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>神忍有以下幾隻</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/014833_bf448f79bcac6b0eddef794992593ebc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F014833_bf448f79bcac6b0eddef794992593ebc.png&h=9b83812b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/014834_68089d2c034278278b61dfb9e20dbfb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F014834_68089d2c034278278b61dfb9e20dbfb0.png&h=d0ee769d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n霸忍<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/015014_5c9d92200019f6269ebd6287d673d1e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F015014_5c9d92200019f6269ebd6287d673d1e7.png&h=107d583d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入手途經pvp一至50/100名，或者儲夠一百張pvp卷去換<br />\n謹記神忍同霸忍係唔可以食5星忍道卷黎升忍道<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/013601_16b5b81acff5df45b65a6d56be2f6641.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F013601_16b5b81acff5df45b65a6d56be2f6641.png&h=65bbde23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新手既你一定會好苦惱，點解角色Lv升得咁慢，其實只要打曜日任何土之卷就可以拎到經驗書幫你既角色升Lv<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/013840_5ced271d787d776fd86a992b561440a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F013840_5ced271d787d776fd86a992b561440a0.png&h=6e80bd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n升Lv升到無錢？唔洗煩<br />\n打日曜關卡就得<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/011433_c270eb7dd0e8b6b2e46e7b8efb3a1362.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F011433_c270eb7dd0e8b6b2e46e7b8efb3a1362.jpg&h=ebb07a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依加3週年，新手們記得拎，無論係老母定其他人用都會二回加一速，好好用，所以記得拎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/152750_af83065c11ef014010cb4f70befe9bd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F152750_af83065c11ef014010cb4f70befe9bd2.png&h=8b54cb02&s={SIZE}\" />新手們唔好見到依張忍道卷平就走去買，因為依張係p幣角專用，比平時d角色食係同食3星忍道卷無分別<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/011448_365827bfb4dc6a8eedae87269a810331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F011448_365827bfb4dc6a8eedae87269a810331.jpg&h=744d444d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依個係天天關岀，依兩個係鳴佐加一速忍具,所以新手們都記得拎<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/011532_0b4a218c4aac2671e59121f32cc06691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F011532_0b4a218c4aac2671e59121f32cc06691.jpg&h=600c3521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依個係曉隊忍具，放落十拳到會令到佢0查，可以達到永動一技同二技，而且放落其他國家忍者到都好高效用，cp值好高既忍具黎"},{"pid":"86bbb01f0d22edf218c075114b6b93e5e3632a5f","tid":887634,"uid":60591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三週年營運已成最大贏家 </span></strong><br />\n營運成功撚到唔少巴打個心都無撚埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">火影眾巴打</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 睇路呀！！！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/79f0f736afc3793115136a6aeac4b74543a9117d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F7Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F79f0f736afc3793115136a6aeac4b74543a9117d.jpg&h=824fc899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>常見日文辭彙 &amp;常見FAQ</strong></span><br />\n可以睇下面條LINK:<br />\n<strong>目錄: </strong>   <br />\n1.常見日文辭彙  <br />\n2.常見FAQ<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1n6aI5pT2