mg.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/26/150125_4b0037e7b5b76dd8ee752cc86d86f0fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F150125_4b0037e7b5b76dd8ee752cc86d86f0fd.png&h=3467be6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/203640_1bfb79d8d2e6519951a199e22bca9e37.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F203640_1bfb79d8d2e6519951a199e22bca9e37.png&h=f2c2171b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">肥毒巴真人(火影博士)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/192817_e5d798ec7f4a702d87eae7fe31ecbb28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F192817_e5d798ec7f4a702d87eae7fe31ecbb28.png&h=4f77f6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">火影有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"01c00330911445381bbe0fee43a07f3714ce1263","tid":887634,"uid":60591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">疾風傳拎石條件</span></strong>(睇以下條link),<br />\n(hard mode 通常夠打就夠條件拎石,如果都係拎唔到可以comment問巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1q7fEGnqTGQ8J-DYAkatpzBb9jLnlSYZVXKDAc5gno9o/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1q7fEGnqTGQ8J-DYAkatpzBb9jLnlSYZVXKDAc5gno9o%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=nfzWDI8azAY8tkzr8OBsXdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1531f55c\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1q7fEGnqTGQ8J-DYAkatpzBb9jLnlSYZVXKDAc5gno9o/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">跟住落黎係巴打嘅心得，包含<del>首抽</del>實用卡、PVP連勝心得</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>巴打嘅心得，包含組隊</strong>睇以下條link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1onxSxavAafUgVWO-qZ782J2VxdPW6Vop4Vx1Vq0lTVI/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1onxSxavAafUgVWO-qZ782J2VxdPW6Vop4Vx1Vq0lTVI%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=nfzWDI8azAY8tkzr8OBsXdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d4d75d2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1onxSxavAafUgVWO-qZ782J2VxdPW6Vop4Vx1Vq0lTVI/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>目錄:</strong> <br />\n1.<span style=\"color: teal;\">無所屬</span>介紹 <strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">(by自稱清泉嘅紫宇宙巴提供)</span></strong><br />\n2.<span style=\"color: gold;\">５0鳴</span>+<span style=\"color: red;\">曉隊</span>介紹 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">(by 征龍)</span></strong><br />\n 3. <span style=\"color: gold;\">PVP 連勝心得</span> <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">(by 征龍)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>屬於連登仔嘅Fd list <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">(by明智巴)</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n(對唔住都要講句<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔歡迎CD-ROM</span></strong>)<br />\n<strong>另外加巴打之前最好講聲先</strong>  除非好熟啦 如果無啦啦有個3唔識7嘅加你 畀著我都拒絕啦 所以最好單聲先 方便大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n曉好需要實力高強嘅忍者，快啲加入我地曉啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/09/eIAYLS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2FeIAYLS.jpg&h=44cd4875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問</span>: 唔小心踩中1001點算?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">答</span>: 開post囉屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咪走咗去呀，唔係嘅話成班巴打排隊搵伯母呀 夜晚無飯食唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n以下係<strong>開post template</strong> (自己copy&amp;paste):<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1FyyNAjj9K2qOZZrQvrRZ45etbqkWJUmS1NJrPy_KqG4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1FyyNAjj9K2qOZZrQvrRZ45etbqkWJUmS1NJrPy_KqG4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=nfzWDI8azAY8tkzr8OBsXdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=5ade0a0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1FyyNAjj9K2qOZZrQvrRZ45etbqkWJUmS1NJrPy_KqG4/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n提下大家GAME入面個個人介紹最好加個LIHKG 等巴打們易認D, 費事好似肥毒博士被人DEL FD都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我喺到感謝所有有份搞POST頭嘅巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋係POST入面有份解答<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><del>伸手</del>新手</strong></span>問題嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該所有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><del>伸手</del>新手黨</span></strong>發問前睇下POST頭嘅資料 真係唔明先再COMMENT問巴打 雖然巴打們都好樂意解答你嘅問題 但唔好一句唔睇扼殺咗咁多位巴打嘅努力同付出  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>肥毒亂舞潮文</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n出新pool，<br />\n十抽唔中，玩家仍然沉得住氣，準備下十抽；肥毒表示冇興趣唔抽。<br />\n廿抽唔中，玩家開始鼓譟；肥毒按兵不動。<br />\n三十抽唔中，玩家開始屌鬼，肥毒改口風表示願意射一抽。<br />\n四十抽唔中，第Ｎ屆反課大聯盟成立；肥毒表示解緊任拎石。<br />\n五十抽唔中，Ｍ仔藍Ｂ開始收手；肥毒表示再諗下抽定唔抽。<br />\n六十抽唔中，玩家ＲＥＦＵＮＤ；課長老吳巴無限巴繼續使出銀彈攻勢，等待限角到來。<br />\n七十抽唔中，玩家開始ＤＥＬ驚；老吳巴抱怨機率太低。<br />\n八十抽唔中，營運停止活動；無限終於說：『老天，好難抽！』<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">肥毒：『我單抽中雙限！』</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後附上火影POST大合照:<br />\n<img src=\"https://scubashackct.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/nassau-2011-Group-at-Shark-Wall.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscubashackct.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F06%2Fnassau-2011-Group-at-Shark-Wall.jpg&h=c5abc82b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"660de031dce32bbcef791424540e06f62664ea6e","tid":887634,"uid":14513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:51:00.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc06522e5df856c8197ae628b1197b954b10ca65","tid":887634,"uid":38391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"Del咗三週年堆嘢先出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff90c08ccf90316efa8ac1034664345b990fda1","tid":887634,"uid":38599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c389c00e3b53024c05f8784a9cba3d80e4422f9e","tid":887634,"uid":60591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"下次再修囉"},{"pid":"7f5f7460f223af75230e18cc5982c5827939603d","tid":887634,"uid":2744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"好懷念編潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef9714a687c3cf82174d8e13cb45044a93e4df4","tid":887634,"uid":33825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T07:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sunfishdivers.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/underwater-group.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsunfishdivers.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F10%2Funderwater-group.jpg&h=82683d66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57ab25f9e171c570e4202dbda8ff9b15b0d6bf8e","tid":887634,"uid":33825,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"最新火影巴打大合照<br />\n<img src=\"https://opers.ucsc.edu/images/scuba-images/Scuba%20Basic%20class%201080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopers.ucsc.edu%2Fimages%2Fscuba-images%2FScuba%2520Basic%2520class%25201080.jpg&h=d459a1d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"150a434a3a41f6fecfcfb4a9b0cad95453065cc3","tid":887634,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0b267a67f5df7ac7451ff77f0465ee99b69c6374","tid":887634,"uid":4312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T07:49:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新手教學內容已更新，請轉去另一post<br />\n<br />\n[I/A]火影忍者 疾風亂舞(153) 只有營運成為大贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/887782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/887782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span></strong>"}]}